<TEXT>
   The Oscar statuette won last year by
Olympia Dukakis for best supporting actress in ``Moonstruck'' has
been stolen from her home.
   Her husband, Louis Zorich, said nothing else apparently was
taken in the May 19 burglary. Police are investigating the theft.
   ``It's curious, puzzling,'' said Zorich, artistic director at
The Whole Theatre in this northeastern New Jersey city. ``It might
