unduly concerned about the loss.
   ``We're not pretentious,'' he said. ``We kept the Oscar in the
kitchen.''
   Ms. Dukakis has asked her agents to inform the Academy of Motion
Picture Arts and Sciences about the theft in the hope of getting a
replacement.
