Correctional Institution on Maryland's Eastern Shore said Crockett
has less than six months to live.
   County Circuit Judge Audrey E. Melbourne leaned into the
ambulance Thursday and quickly suspended the remainder of
Crockett's sentence. He will return to his mother's home in
Washington, D.C..
   Crockett's mother called Melbourne several weeks ago and asked
her to reconsider Crockett's sentence.
