<TEXT>
   The stock market gained ground today in fairly
quiet pre-holiday trading.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials rose 8.06 to 2,490.65 by
11 a.m. on Wall Street.
   Gainers outnumbered losers by about 9 to 5 in nationwide trading
of New York Stock Exchange-listed issues, with 734 up, 397 down and
